Package: RNAseqDEGAnalysis
Type: Shiny Application
Title: RNA-seq Differential Gene Expression Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Eren Ada, PhD
Maintainer: Eren Ada <eren.ada@example.com>
Description: A comprehensive Shiny application for differential gene expression 
    analysis of RNA-seq data using DESeq2. Provides guided workflow from data 
    upload through result export.
